### Separate AG buffer implemented (Entry 45)

`MORI_SEPARATE_AG_BUFFER=1` makes SDMA AG write into a separate internal
symmetric buffer instead of overwriting the scatter/reduce transit. This safely
skips waiting on peers' reduce_complete flags before AG because AG no longer
corrupts peer reduce input. Default off; test pending.

### Multi-q SDMA AG implemented (Entry 40)

`MORI_MULTI_Q_AG=1` distributes AG chunks over qId `1 + c % min(numQ-1,15)`
instead of serializing all chunks on qId=1. Host tracks per-q AG generation
counters to avoid unsafe signal resets. Default path unchanged. This targets
the ~1ms AG wait seen in continuous phase timing.

### Plan A v1 实测 (Entry 20, **已知不是 pipelined 实现**)

| 变体 | overlap wall | seq_ar | seq_gemm | overlap/seq_gemm | vs RCCL |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Plan A (SDMA copy + DIRECT_OUTPUT=1)** | **9.084 ms** | 5.845 | 4.129 | 2.200 | **+21.1% (+1.58ms WORSE)** |
| SDMA no-copy | 7.355 ms | 4.801 | 3.991 | 1.843 | -2.0% |
| RCCL today | 7.503 ms | 5.133 | 3.977 | 1.887 | — |

vs Entry 19 BASELINE 7.802 ms: **Plan A v1 慢 1.28 ms**.

### Plan A v1 失败的直接实现原因

Entry 20 的 Plan A v1 K2 实现不是 user 要的 "CU pipelined"：它串行执行
`reduce(c) -> barrier(c) -> XGMI_pull(c) -> reduce(c+1)`，没有让
`pull(c)` 和 `reduce(c+1)` 并行。因此 Entry 20 的 "CU-as-AG 体系失败"
结论不能直接用于否定 Plan A v2。

### Plan A v2 当前实现 (Entry 21)

K2 已拆成：
- Block 0: orchestration (`chunks_complete` wait + cross-PE barrier + `ag_sync`)
- R-group: reduce chunk c -> `transit[myPe slot]`
- A-group: wait `ag_sync(c)` -> XGMI pull chunk c -> `user_output`

这样恢复目标流水：
`R-group reduce(c+1)` 与 `A-group pull(c)` 并行。

Plan A v2 也考虑 CU 争用：
- `MORI_PLAN_A_CU` default **96** (不再默认吃满 160 compute blocks)
- `MORI_PLAN_A_NR` default `CU/3`, A-group 获得约 2/3 blocks
- host clamp `nA >= npes`

### 仍需验证的风险 (不是结论)

**架构错配**: Plan A 把 AG 从独立 SDMA engine 搬到 CU. 在 GEMM overlap 场景下, Plan A 的 AR 阶段和 GEMM 抢 CU.

**机制 1 (seq_ar +0.66ms)**: BASELINE 用 SDMA AG, CU 在 chunk c+1 reduce 时 SDMA 同时做 chunk c AG (chunk pipeline depth 2). Plan A CU AG 占 CU, chunk c+1 reduce 必须等 chunk c AG pull 完成 (depth 1).

**机制 2 (overlap +1.28ms)**: per-AR CU 占用越多, GEMM overlap 退化越严重. 单调关系 (4 个数据点验证):

| algorithm | per-AR CU 占用 | overlap/seq_gemm |
|---|---|---|
| RCCL ring (sparse) | ~14 × 0.05 ms 间歇 | **1.89** (最低) |
| BASELINE (SDMA AG) | reduce only ~0.30 ms | **2.12** |
| **Plan A** (CU pull AG + write) | reduce + barrier + pull + write ~1.0 ms | **2.20** |
| Plan B (CU push + CU copy) | reduce + push + copy ~0.95 ms | **2.44** (最高) |

**这仍是 Plan A v2 的主要风险**，但必须用 v2 的 R/A-group pipeline + lower CU cap 实测，不能拿 v1 的串行实现直接下结论。

